# SettleFlow Frontend Rules

Follow `docs/frontend-plan.md` exactly. Start only after backend B7 is complete.

## Stack (Locked)

shadcn/ui · TanStack Query v5 · TanStack Table · Recharts · Framer Motion · Lucide · Tailwind v4

- Server Components by default; `"use client"` only when needed
- **No Polaris** — App Bridge for session tokens only
- No Redux, SWR, or hand-rolled UI primitives

## Architecture

- API types from OpenAPI/Zod — never hand-duplicate
- All fetch via `lib/api-client.ts` (envelope + auth headers)
- Shared page components in `components/`; only `layout/` shells differ (embedded vs standalone)
- **Do not modify backend code**

## Design

Black & white neutral palette; color only for status (green/yellow/red; blue for primary CTA).
Customize shadcn via CSS variables only — do not edit component source.
